tsl / toggleshortlink         Toggles detection of short weblinks

   Format:
      ;tsl                    Toggles detection of short weblinks

   Notes:
      Many parts of the Axmud code, particularly the code dealing with text
         received from the world, auto-detects weblinks like
         'http://deathmud.com' and makes them clickable.
      Axmud can also detect short weblinks like 'deathmud.com'. Dection of
         short links is turned on by default, can be turned off with this
         command.

   User commands:
      tsl / togglelink / toggleshortlink
